===ᱯᱩᱞᱤᱥ ᱥᱴᱮᱥᱚᱱ===
ᱫᱩᱨᱜᱟᱯᱩᱨ ᱯᱩᱞᱤᱥ ᱥᱴᱮᱥᱚᱱ, ᱫᱩᱨᱜᱟᱯᱩᱨ ᱥᱴᱤᱞ ᱴᱟᱣᱩᱱᱥᱤᱯ ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱟᱨᱵᱤᱸᱫᱚ ᱮᱣᱮᱱᱭᱩ ᱨᱮ ᱢᱮᱱᱟᱜᱼᱟ, [[ᱟᱱᱰᱟᱞ]] ᱥᱤᱰᱤ ᱵᱞᱚᱠ ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱠᱮᱡ ᱴᱷᱟᱶ ᱨᱮ jurisdiction ᱢᱮᱱᱟᱜᱼᱟ ᱾ ᱱᱟᱯᱟᱭ ᱴᱚᱴᱷᱟ ᱘᱐&nbsp;ᱠᱤᱞᱚᱢᱤᱴᱚᱨ<sup>᱒</sup> ᱨᱮ ᱢᱮᱱᱟᱜᱼᱟ ᱟᱨ ᱦᱚᱲ ᱮᱞ ᱒᱙᱒,᱘᱔᱑ ᱜᱟᱱ ᱢᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱠᱚᱣᱟ ᱾<ref name=ps1>{{cite web  | url = http://wbpspm.gov.in/publications/District%20Statistical%20Handbook | title = District Statistical Handbook 2014 Bardhaman  | work = Tables 2.1, 2.2  | publisher = Department of Statistics and Programme Implementation, Government of West Bengal  | accessdate = 23 September 2018  | }}</ref><ref name=ps2>{{cite web| url = http://asansoldurgapurpolice.in/#  |title = Asansol Durgapur Police Commissionerate  |work = Find your police station  | publisher= Asansol Durgapur Police | accessdate = 18 February 2017}}</ref>

